\"#feedbackModal_main_2534461\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 23, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zii1665702717603.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zii1665702717603.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zii1665702717603.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zii1665702717603\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ProcScript Tracing Messages\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">When the Debugger tracing setting is set to value <code class=\"ph codeph\">16</code> (trace all activate information), the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> information for the some errors appears in the message frame.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zii1665702717603__section_w1345ab1b5b1_w1346ab1b5_w1347ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Errors Sent to Message Frame when <code class=\"ph codeph\">traceprint = 16</code>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-50</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_SIGNATURE&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__3\">\n Signature descriptor for the current component not found (in UAR or resource file). For example, the component name provided is not valid.\n <p class=\"p\">Signature descriptor found, but an interface is missing or invalid.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-51</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_SIGNATURE_ID&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__3\">\n The identifier of the compiled component does not match the identifier in the signature descriptor (in UAR or resource file).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-58</code></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_COMPONENT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zii1665702717603__table_d2150e1_d2151e1_d2152e1__entry__3\">\n The named component cannot be found.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534461\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534461\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ProcScript Tracing Messages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ProcScript Tracing Messages When the Debugger tracing setting is set to value 16 (trace all activate information), the $procerrorcontext information for the some errors appears in the message frame. Table 1. Errors Sent to Message Frame when traceprint = 16 Value Error constant Meaning -50 <UACTERR_NO_SIGNATURE> Signature descriptor for the current component not found (in UAR or resource file). For example, the component name provided is not valid. Signature descriptor found, but an interface is missing or invalid. -51 <UACTERR_SIGNATURE_ID> The identifier of the compiled component does not match the identifier in the signature descriptor (in UAR or resource file). -58 <UACTERR_NO_COMPONENT> The named component cannot be found. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}